description:
The "Freedom" art exhibit is more than just another article to censor, for the Betterment Force--it`s an insult to their honor. The coming battle at Ibaraki is set to be worse than anything the Kanto Defense Force has seen before!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Struggle to the Death! Ibaraki Prefecture Defense Exhibit
